OL,7,FOne of its founders, Joy Killip, set
OL,8,Fup the Talking Newspaper in 1977 as a
OL,9,Fway to provide blind people with the
OL,10,Finformation they needed.
OL,12,FShe said: "It's so important because
OL,13,Fthe blind can easily be cut off with
OL,14,Fnothing.
OL,16,F"They can't read the local news, they
OL,17,Fcan hear but they can't read."
