OL,7,FAfter hearing about a similar project
OL,8,Fin, Joy worked with The Blackpool,
OL,9,FFylde, and Wyre Society for the Blind,
OL,10,Falso known as N-Vision, to launch
OL,11,Ftheir own version.
OL,13,FShe said: "We formed a committee and
OL,14,Fmade our first news tape on a home
OL,15,Frecorder. It was barely acceptable,
OL,16,Fbut over the years we've got a decent
OL,17,Frecorder."
