OL,7,FAlmost 50 years on, the Talking
OL,8,FNewspaper now operates from a
OL,9,Fprofessional recording studio, and
OL,10,Fprovides 10 hours of audio a week to
OL,11,Froughly 200 listeners.
OL,13,FThe station's founder Joy still reads
OL,14,Fout the news for listeners, and on
OL,15,FTuesday 2 April she celebrated her
OL,16,F100th birthday alongside her fellow
OL,17,Fvolunteers.
