OL,7,FShe said: "This keeps my brain alive,
OL,8,Fit keeps me alive. It give me
OL,9,Fsomething to live for and I enjoy it
OL,10,Fbecause I know how much it means to
OL,11,Fvisually impaired people.
OL,13,F"I get letters saying 'I like what you
OL,14,Fread'."
OL,16,FAs a surprise for her 100th birthday,
OL,17,Fthe latest edition of the Talking
OL,18,FNewspaper featured an article
OL,19,Fdedicated to Joy's hard work.
