OL,7,FA volunteer read out: "Since 1966, Joy
OL,8,Fhas volunteered continuously for the
OL,9,Forganisation and still devotes several
OL,10,Fhours each and every week.
OL,12,F"This is more years and commitment
OL,13,Fthan the average person gives to paid
OL,14,Femployment.
OL,16,F"Happy 100 years Birthday Joy. You are
OL,17,Fa true superstar and an inspiration,
OL,18,Fand deserve the highest recognition
OL,19,Ffor your service to your local
OL,20,Fcommunity in Lancashire. Happy
OL,21,Fbirthday."
