OL,7,FN-Visions communications officer,
OL,8,FGarry Green, says the Talking
OL,9,FNewspaper continues to be an important
OL,10,Fservice half a century on, even as
OL,11,Fpodcasts and audiobooks continue to
OL,12,Fmake news and entertainment more
OL,13,Faccessible.
OL,15,FHe said: "People want to connect with
OL,16,Fwhat's happening in their local
OL,17,Fneighbourhood, in their community. We
OL,18,Frecord the local newspapers, but many
OL,19,Fother things like magazines.
